<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="200800000t" end="229600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">我是第二〇三航空魔导大队</p>
<p begin="229600000t" end="254600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">坦妮婭·冯·徳古雷查夫少校</p>
<p begin="262500000t" end="284200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">我要见泽图亚阁下</p>
<p begin="288800000t" end="305500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">少校啊</p>
<p begin="305500000t" end="338800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">非常抱歉 阁下现在外出了</p>
<p begin="341800000t" end="362200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">那么鲁德斯多夫阁下昵</p>
<p begin="379300000t" end="436400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">太抱歉了 参谋部全员都外出了</p>
<p begin="449400000t" end="470200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">是有什么重要的会议吗</p>
<p begin="470200000t" end="496100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">大概是都去宴厅了吧</p>
<p begin="504000000t" end="517400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">宴厅？</p>
<p begin="519900000t" end="554100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">诸位阁下都大喊庆祝着胜利的美酒什么的</p>
<p begin="559100000t" end="587400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">可以的话 真希望我也能加入他们</p>
<p begin="587400000t" end="600800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">但这也太不现实了</p>
<p begin="689200000t" end="703800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">发生什么事了吗</p>
<p begin="703800000t" end="710000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">在</p>
<p begin="711300000t" end="725900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">我指的是德古雷查夫少校</p>
<p begin="729600000t" end="747600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">不 并没什么事…</p>
<p begin="750100000t" end="778000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">说是想见泽图亚阁下</p>
<p begin="781800000t" end="802600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">我们告诉了她酒宴的事情</p>
<p begin="867700000t" end="885200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">德古雷查夫少校</p>
<p begin="971100000t" end="999900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">第十二话 胜利的用法</p>
<p begin="1109200000t" end="1128400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">记得你不加牛奶和砂糖…</p>
<p begin="1133400000t" end="1155900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">是的 不需要</p>
<p begin="1235600000t" end="1248100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">味道果然不同啊</p>
<p begin="1268900000t" end="1288500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">这是纪念胜利的达乐麦耶</p>
<p begin="1295600000t" end="1315200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">可是特供品哦</p>
<p begin="1348200000t" end="1375300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">你好像去拜访了泽图亚阁下吧</p>
<p begin="1385300000t" end="1417800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">这次胜利 你功不可没</p>
<p begin="1425800000t" end="1446200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">有什么要谏言的话</p>
<p begin="1446200000t" end="1469600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">还请直言不讳</p>
<p begin="1479600000t" end="1507900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">直言不讳吗…</p>
<p begin="1515400000t" end="1524600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">怎么了…</p>
<p begin="1524600000t" end="1568400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">我军确实是打了一场精彩的胜仗</p>
<p begin="1577200000t" end="1633900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">想必现在全世界都已经对我军的勇猛膛目结舌了</p>
<p begin="1636000000t" end="1660600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">帝国的胜利和荣耀</p>
<p begin="1660600000t" end="1698500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">也许只有这一瞬间才是货真价实的</p>
<p begin="1706900000t" end="1720600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">这一瞬间？</p>
<p begin="1744000000t" end="1785300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">胜利 这是何等魅惑之物</p>
<p begin="1787000000t" end="1827400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">没有人不对这坛美酒馋涎欲滴 这是理所当然的</p>
<p begin="1827400000t" end="1893700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">但是为什么参谋总部不去活用胜利呢</p>
<p begin="1940400000t" end="1959600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">少校去了参谋总部？</p>
<p begin="1964600000t" end="2003000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">看她那个气势 说不定闹进去了</p>
<p begin="2005100000t" end="2025100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">不过 不用担心太多</p>
<p begin="2030500000t" end="2047600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">但是她显然和平常不一样</p>
<p begin="2047600000t" end="2098900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">没关系的 我无法想象少校会违反军纪</p>
<p begin="2102300000t" end="2133500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">说不定现在已经在晚餐室喝着红酒…</p>
<p begin="2133500000t" end="2149400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">啊 这不太可能</p>
<p begin="2153600000t" end="2174400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">谁带药膏了啊</p>
<p begin="2174400000t" end="2187800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">我被太阳晒过头了</p>
<p begin="2187800000t" end="2216500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">我记得泰亚尼准尉的遗留品里有</p>
<p begin="2385000000t" end="2406300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">不活用胜利？</p>
<p begin="2406300000t" end="2462600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">请恕下官直言 我军参谋总部虽然知道如何胜利</p>
<p begin="2462600000t" end="2498500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">但却不知如何使用胜利</p>
<p begin="2506800000t" end="2521400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">这是什么意思</p>
<p begin="2525200000t" end="2585190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">参谋总部的各位好像正沉醉于胜利的美酒之中吧</p>
<p begin="2599400000t" end="2682000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">当然了 在前线尽完义务的将士也是有权利讴歌片刻欢愉的吧</p>
<p begin="2710400000t" end="2786300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">但是连执行战争指导的上级将官都天真忘我地沉醉</p>
<p begin="2789600000t" end="2814200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">这已是怠慢和失策</p>
<p begin="2814200000t" end="2847200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">毫无疑问已是犯罪性质的无作为</p>
<p begin="2855900000t" end="2883900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">少校 适可而止吧</p>
<p begin="2887200000t" end="2906400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">话说的越界了</p>
<p begin="2910600000t" end="2951400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">是中校您说的直言不讳</p>
<p begin="2953500000t" end="3004800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">就算军神玛尔斯眷顾着你 这话也太傲慢了</p>
<p begin="3010700000t" end="3055300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">恕下官直言 神灵的眷顾于我没有丝毫…</p>
<p begin="3125000000t" end="3185000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">虽说贵官是拥有卓越先见能力和判断能力的稀世天才将官</p>
<p begin="3192100000t" end="3231300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">果然人的本性是不会变的</p>
<p begin="3347700000t" end="3373100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">关于你抗命未遂一事</p>
<p begin="3374400000t" end="3404000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">西方军来投诉了</p>
<p begin="3411500000t" end="3462400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">下官只是想要执行授权范围内的行动</p>
<p begin="3462400000t" end="3502400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">我知道你不是会违反军纪的军人</p>
<p begin="3507000000t" end="3551200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">但话又说回来 参谋总部给了你权限</p>
<p begin="3555000000t" end="3583700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">不是为了让你增加现场的摩擦</p>
<p begin="3589600000t" end="3614200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">以军功为荣无可厚非</p>
<p begin="3614200000t" end="3644600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">但不要以为全是自己的功劳</p>
<p begin="3649200000t" end="3675900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">共和国的首都已经被占领了</p>
<p begin="3685100000t" end="3725100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">继续抗战可以说是毫无意义 甚至有害</p>
<p begin="3763100000t" end="3802300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">我们还有什么理由继续进行战争</p>
<p begin="3805600000t" end="3823600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">对于近现代的国家而言</p>
<p begin="3824400000t" end="3851100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">军队是国家的暴力装置</p>
<p begin="3851100000t" end="3908700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">若不惜以牺牲国家继续战斗 只能说是疯狂至极</p>
<p begin="3914100000t" end="3936200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">正是你所说</p>
<p begin="3939900000t" end="3990000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">既然如此 为什么你主张战争将会继续</p>
<p begin="4009600000t" end="4035400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">请恕下官直言</p>
<p begin="4037500000t" end="4068800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">泽图亚阁下和鲁德斯多夫阁下</p>
<p begin="4068800000t" end="4112600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">乃是精通政治和军事的合理实用主义者</p>
<p begin="4114700000t" end="4134300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">他们是伟大的军人</p>
<p begin="4141000000t" end="4170600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">从这点讲 中校您也是同类</p>
<p begin="4178900000t" end="4201000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">逻辑与知识的大本营</p>
<p begin="4209400000t" end="4244000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">这正是我帝国军参谋本部</p>
<p begin="4260300000t" end="4300300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">因此所有人都以合理性为根本</p>
<p begin="4300300000t" end="4327000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">坚信着战争即将终结</p>
<p begin="4327000000t" end="4382000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">可是 我只能说这是不完全的合理性</p>
<p begin="4396600000t" end="4423800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">不完全的…合理性？</p>
<p begin="4432500000t" end="4480100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">参谋本部的各位实在是太合理了</p>
<p begin="4485900000t" end="4520100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">所以才会完全疏忽了</p>
<p begin="4526800000t" end="4604800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">人类是不单凭合理性行动的愚蠢生物这一点</p>
<p begin="4618100000t" end="4686900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">贵官是想说我们人类至今仍是缺乏理性的野兽吗！</p>
<p begin="4694400000t" end="4748700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">若要冒着语病的风险 我完全就是这个意思</p>
<p begin="4754900000t" end="4777900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">你有什么根据敢如此断言</p>
<p begin="4786200000t" end="4802900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">是历史</p>
<p begin="4810400000t" end="4845400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">准确说 是我自己的历史</p>
<p begin="4850400000t" end="4875500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">这也是我个人的经历</p>
<p begin="4897600000t" end="4910500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">说来听听</p>
<p begin="4936300000t" end="4955500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">我经历过来了</p>
<p begin="4957200000t" end="4998900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">人们被憎恨支配燃烧的双眼</p>
<p begin="5004300000t" end="5059000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">以及优秀的部下被愤怒冲昏头脑 失去冷静的瞬间</p>
<p begin="5067700000t" end="5127800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">这些都是被憎恶支配着的复仇的轮回</p>
<p begin="5135300000t" end="5159900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">因此下官领悟到了</p>
<p begin="5163200000t" end="5215390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">不 与其说领悟 不如说回忆起来了</p>
<p begin="5227500000t" end="5293800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">我曾经亲身领受到了反对合理主义的疯狂报复</p>
<p begin="5308800000t" end="5336700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">不论近代化如何进步</p>
<p begin="5336700000t" end="5369700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">不论社会规范如何渗透</p>
<p begin="5369700000t" end="5401000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">人类 是会在特殊情况下抛弃合理</p>
<p begin="5401000000t" end="5446400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">优先感情的愚蠢存在</p>
<p begin="5539000000t" end="5584500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">人类一旦被憎恨支配 不论是算计还是合理性</p>
<p begin="5584500000t" end="5622900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">连得失都会抛在脑后一心反抗到底</p>
<p begin="5649600000t" end="5691300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">正因如此 下官才不得不谏言</p>
<p begin="5735100000t" end="5784300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">我们不该沉醉于虚渺的胜利之中</p>
<p begin="5789700000t" end="5834700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">憎恨的火苗必须全数扑灭</p>
<p begin="5891900000t" end="5905200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">失…失礼了</p>
<p begin="5908600000t" end="5936100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">虽然还是调查中的情报</p>
<p begin="5939000000t" end="5972800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">南方大陆有共和国残军动向</p>
<p begin="6098800000t" end="6137500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">我作为深爱自由的共和国市民</p>
<p begin="6142600000t" end="6173800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">作为光荣的共和国市民</p>
<p begin="6173800000t" end="6180900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">宣誓！</p>
<p begin="6193000000t" end="6203400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">直到胜利为止</p>
<p begin="6207600000t" end="6239300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">我们绝不放下武器</p>
<p begin="6250600000t" end="6304400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">我们的战友也将并肩作战</p>
<p begin="6309400000t" end="6349400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">世界的命运落在了我们的肩上</p>
<p begin="6371100000t" end="6394100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">因此 我现在…</p>
<p begin="6411200000t" end="6461600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">代表祖国 作为自由共和国的一员</p>
<p begin="6472000000t" end="6534600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">在此宣言对帝国的彻底抗战</p>
<p begin="6613400000t" end="6641400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">与此同时           帝都柏恩</p>
<p begin="6649300000t" end="6675600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">共和国还役沦陷吗</p>
<p begin="6678900000t" end="6705200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">可恶 军队到底在搞什么</p>
<p begin="6710200000t" end="6736900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">约翰 一直都没联系</p>
<p begin="6739000000t" end="6762300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">战争还要继续吗</p>
<p begin="6775300000t" end="6792400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">帝国陆军新闻</p>
<p begin="6794500000t" end="6817000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">下午三时的战时情报</p>
<p begin="6818200000t" end="6840300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">赶快去进攻南方大陆啊</p>
