<p begin="13710100000t" end="13731800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">不过想必无需…</p>
<p begin="13738100000t" end="13765200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">无需您丝毫的担忧！</p>
<p begin="13773900000t" end="13813100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">我们的战场上可没有狗屁神灵的容身之处！</p>
<p begin="13814000000t" end="13855700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">是时候让我们来接替神灵的工作了</p>
<p begin="13855700000t" end="13903600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">就由我等士卒替天行道吧！</p>
<p begin="13906600000t" end="13943700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">让傲慢不逊的神灵尝尝失业是何滋味！</p>
<p begin="13974500000t" end="13982500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">是！</p>
<p begin="13991600000t" end="14019600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">恕我冒昧直言…</p>
<p begin="14028300000t" end="14065100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">那是披着幼女之皮的…</p>
<p begin="14085100000t" end="14098800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">…怪物！</p>
<p begin="14103800000t" end="14124300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">听好了 战友们</p>
<p begin="14125500000t" end="14145500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">开战了</p>
<p begin="14145500000t" end="14165500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293"></p>
